<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1301334>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Live photo of the paratype Cyrtodactylus tanahjampea sp. nov. (MVZ.267744). Photo: J A. McGuire." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1301334/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1301336>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Detailed illustrations on head of the holotype of Cyrtodactylus tanahjampea sp. nov. (MZB.Lace.5675). (A) Above view of head. (B) Lateral view of head. (C) Snout region, showing rostral and post rostrals scales. (D) Ventral view of head. Bars = 10 mm. Photos by A. Riyanto" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1301336/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1301338>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Comparation on femoral and cloacal region between male and female of Cyrtodactylus tanahjampea sp. (A) Male, holotype, MZB.Lace.5675, showing precloaccofemoral pores and lack precloacal depression. (B) Female, paratype, lack precloacofemoral pores and groove. Bar = 10 mm. Photos by A. Riyanto." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1301338/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1301340>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Habitat of Cyrtodactylus tanahjampea sp. nov. Photo by J. A. McGuire." ;
